Item 5.    Other Events
        On February 23, 2004, Amphenol Corporation (the "Company") entered into an Underwriting Agreement dated February 23, 2004 (the "Underwriting Agreement"), with Morgan Stanley & Co. Incorporated, Citigroup Global Markets Inc. and UBS Securities LLC and the other several underwriters named on Schedule I thereto (collectively, the "Underwriters") and certain stockholders named therein (the "Selling Stockholders"), with respect to the offer and sale by the Selling Stockholders and the purchase by the Underwriters, of 8,000,000 shares of the Company's Class A common stock, par value $.001 per share, with an option to purchase from certain of the Selling Stockholders up to an additional 1,200,000 shares of common stock to cover over-allotments, if any.
        The form of the Underwriting Agreement is attached as Exhibit 1.1 hereto. The press release relating to the pricing of the 8,000,000 shares of common stock is filed as Exhibit 99.1 to this Current Report on Form 8-K.
