as soon as practicable and in any event no later than 60 days after the beginning of each fiscal year, consolidated operating and related budgets for the Company and its Subsidiaries for each fiscal quarter of such fiscal year, in reasonable detail as customarily prepared by management of the Company for its internal use and setting forth an explanation of the principal assumptions on which such budgets are based;
