Item 2.02 Results of Operations and Financial Condition
 
On October 19, 2005, Amphenol Corporation issued a press release setting forth Amphenol Corporation's third quarter 2005 earnings. A copy of Amphenol Corporation's press release is attached hereto as Exhibit 99.1.
 
As provided in General Instruction B.2 of Form 8-K, the information and exhibits contained in this Form 8-K shall not be deemed to be "filed" for purposes of Section 18 of the Securities Exchange Act of 1934, as amended, nor shall they be deemed to be incorporated by reference in any filing under the Securities Act of 1933, as amended, except as shall be expressly set forth by specific reference in such a filing.
 
Item 9.01. Financial Statements, Proforma Financial Information and Exhibits
 
99.1 Press Release, dated October 19, 2005, issued by Amphenol Corporation
Signature
 
