O.    RELATED PARTY TRANSACTIONS
 
Related Party Revenue
 
Connection Systems' revenue from sales of products to the Parent was $29.0 million for the year ended December 31, 2004. The cost of products for the sales to the Parent was $26.3 million for the year ended December 31, 2004. The combined balance sheet of Connection Systems includes accounts receivable from related party of $2.1 million as of December 31, 2004 from the sales of products to the Parent.
 
Parent Allocations
 
