.  At or prior to the issuance of any Securities within a Series, the following shall be established (as to such Series generally, in the case of , and either as to the Securities within such Series or as to such Series generally, in the case of ) pursuant to a Board Resolution, and set forth or determined in the manner provided in a Board Resolution, an Officers' Certificate or a Supplemental Indenture:
