Section 8.1
                                     
Option to Effect Legal Defeasance or Covenant Defeasance
.  The Company may, at its option evidenced by a Board Resolution or an Officers' Certificate, at any time, with respect to the Securities of any Series, elect to have either or be applied to all of the outstanding Securities of such Series upon compliance with the conditions set forth below in this Article VIII.
