AMPHENOL ANNOUNCES
FIRST QUARTER 2010 DIVIDEND PAYMENT
 
Wallingford, Connecticut.  January 29, 2010.  Amphenol Corporation (NYSE-APH) confirmed today that its Board of Directors approved a continuing quarterly dividend on its Common Stock in the amount of $.015 per share at its meeting held on January 28, 2010.  The Company will pay its first quarter dividend for 2010 on or about April 7, 2010 to shareholders of record as of March 17, 2010.
 
