.  The Company will prepare a final term sheet containing only a description of the Notes, in a form approved by the Underwriters and attached as hereto, and will file such term sheet pursuant to Rule 433(d) under the Securities Act within the time required by such rule (such term sheet, the "").  Any such Final Term Sheet is an Issuer Free Writing Prospectus for purposes of this Agreement.
