Item 2.02 Results of Operations and Financial Condition.
 
On April 25, 2013, Amphenol Corporation (the "Company") issued a press release announcing its second quarter dividend for 2013 on its Common Stock in the amount of $.105 per share. A copy of Amphenol Corporation's related press release is attached hereto as Exhibit 99.1.
 
